// ABOUT
about-text: <span class="firstcharacter">H</span>ouse Marija is a family owned apartment house located in the small town of Brbinj on the island of Dugi Otok. With it's four apartments it is conveniently located on the tip of cove Jaz, only 20 m from the sea, and 200 m from the beach. It offers an excellent surrounding for a peaceful and relaxing vacation. Each apartment has a spacious terrace overlooking the sea, prefect for enjoying your daily meal or a glass of wine in the evening. Apartments are around 50 m<sup>2</sup> each and have two separate bedrooms and a dining room with a fully equipped kitchen. Plenty of parking space for personal vehicles is available right next to the house and there is also a possibility of setting a smaller boat to berth. Close at hand, one can find a few cozy restaurants, a small grocery store and a post office. The town is connected with Zadar by ferry operating multiple times a day.

